    {# What is so-sure? #}
    <section class="section--pad homepage--what-is-so-sure">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <h2 class="h1">What is so-sure?</h2>
                    <p class="lead">When insurance started in 17th century it was great: when you claimed you had customer red carpet treatment and when there were no claims, you got money back!</p>
