                    <p class="lead">If you are honest, we have your back. If not, go elsewhere. We provide a better service because we trust our customers are honest. This also means that we take fraud and dishonest customers very seriously and are ruthless with them because they increase the cost of insurance for everyone else.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <div class="img-container">
                        <img src="data:image/png;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAD/ACwAAAAAAQABAAACADs="
                             data-src="{{ cdn_url }}/images/homepage/so-sure_what-is-so-sure.svg"
                             alt="What is so-sure?"
                             class="img-responsive img-responsive--center so-sure_homepage-what-is-so-sure">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

