                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <ol class="ol--blue-counter">
                        <li>
                            <h3 class="text-blue">We don’t hide behind the small print and painful claims process</h3>
                            <p>We’re upfront and honest with our customers on what is covered, what is not, and what the claims process looks like. This means that there’s no nasty surprises when you have an issue with your device. You don’t need a law degree to understand our policy - everything is explained in plain English.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <h3 class="text-blue">If something bad happens, we aim to provide next day repair or replacement</h3>
                            <p>As simple as that. It sucks to be without your phone, we understand it and work with a global phone provider and world-class logistics company who help us get a model back in your hands the next working day.</p>
                        </li>
