                    <p>These helpful people are here in the UK, available to answer your call 24-hrs a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. Just call them on <a name="Contact the claims team on - 0344 856 0852" href="tel:0344 856 0852"><span class="sr-only">Call our claims team on: </span><strong>0344 856 0852</strong></a>.</p>
